{"title_page": "Guillermo Bongiorno", "text_new": "{{short description|Argentine cyclist}}\n{{Infobox cyclist\n| name           = Guillermo Bongiorno\n| image          = Guillermo_Bongiorno.jpg\n| image_size     = 250px\n| caption        = Bongiorno at the [[2009 Danmark Rundt]]\n| fullname       = Guillermo Rub\u00e9n Bongiorno\n| nickname       =\n| birth_date     = {{bda|1978|7|29|df=y}}\n| birth_place    = [[Mar del Plata]], [[Argentina]]\n| currentteam    = Retired\n| discipline     = [[Road cycling|Road]]\n| role           = Rider\n| ridertype      = Sprinter\n| amateuryears1  = 2001\u20132002\n| amateurteam1   = Parolin\u2013Uniconfort\n| amateuryears2  = 2013\u20132014\n| amateurteam2   = Sprint Haupt\n| amateuryears3  = 2014\u20132016\n| amateurteam3   = Buenos Aires Ciudad\n| amateuryears4  = 2017\n| amateurteam4   = Expo Ladrillos\u2013Luj\u00e1n\n| proyears1      = 2003\u20132009\n| proteam1       = {{ct|BRD|2003}}\n| proyears2      = 2010\n| proteam2       = {{ct|LGS|2010}}\n| proyears3      = 2011\n| proteam3       = {{ct|AMO|2011}}\n| majorwins      =\n| medaltemplates =\n| show-medals    =\n}}\n'''Guillermo Rub\u00e9n Bongiorno''' (born 29 July 1978 in [[Mar del Plata]]) is an Argentine former professional cyclist.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.procyclingstats.com/rider.php?id=122530 | title=Guillermo Rub\u00e9n Bongiorno | publisher=Pro Cycling Stats | accessdate=8 February 2016}}</ref>\n\n==Major results==\n{{div col|colwidth=30em}}\n;2003\n:1st Stage 10 [[Tour de Langkawi]]\n;2004\n:1st Stage 10 [[Tour de Langkawi]]\n;2005\n:1st [[Gran Premio Citt\u00e0 di Misano \u2013 Adriatico]]\n:1st [[Giro della Provincia di Reggio Calabria]]\n: [[Tour de Langkawi]]\n::1st Stages 2 & 6\n:1st Stage 1a [[Settimana Internazionale di Coppi e Bartali]]\n:1st Stage 1 [[Settimana Ciclistica Lombarda]]\n:1st Stage 2a [[Brixia Tour]]\n:1st Stage 1 [[Regio-Tour]]\n;2006\n:1st Stage 2 [[Tour de Langkawi]]\n;2008\n:1st Stage 1 [[Tour of Turkey]]\n: [[Danmark Rundt]]\n: